SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5430
A bill to amend 1978 PA 368, entitled
"Public health code,"
by amending section 12501 (MCL 333.12501), as amended by 2004 PA
408, and by adding section 12510a.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 12501. (1) As used in sections 12501 to 12516:
2 (a) "Campground" means a parcel or tract of land under the
3 control of a person in which sites are offered for the use of the
4 public or members of an organization, either free of charge or for
5 a fee, for the establishment of temporary living quarters for 5 or
6 more recreational units. Campground does not include a seasonal
7 mobile home park licensed under the mobile home commission act,
8 1987 PA 96, MCL 125.2301 to 125.2349.125.2350.
